{
  "page": "Alys Rivers's son",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Alys Rivers's son</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">Aemond Targaryen</a> (alleged)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers\" title=\"Alys Rivers\">Alys Rivers</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Alys Rivers's son</b> was a boy claimed by <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers\" title=\"Alys Rivers\">Alys Rivers</a> to be her child by Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">Aemond Targaryen</a>. His given name is unknown.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alys_Rivers%27s_son&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">Aemond Targaryen</a> ordered the deaths of the remaining members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Strong\" title=\"House Strong\">House Strong</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonrider\" title=\"Dragonrider\">dragonrider</a> spared the life of <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers\" title=\"Alys Rivers\">Alys Rivers</a>, however, and took the older <a href=\"/index.php/Wet_nurse\" title=\"Wet nurse\">wet nurse</a> for his bedmate as a spoil of war.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Eustace_(Dance_of_the_Dragons)\" title=\"Eustace (Dance of the Dragons)\">Eustace</a> disagrees with <a href=\"/index.php/Mushroom\" title=\"Mushroom\">Mushroom</a>'s claim that Alys used <a href=\"/index.php/Love_potion\" title=\"Love potion\">love potions</a> and philtres to entice Aemond and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>While Criston marched south along the <a href=\"/index.php/Gods_Eye\" title=\"Gods Eye\">Gods Eye</a>, Aemond began burning the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> with <a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a>. When Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Sabitha_Frey\" title=\"Sabitha Frey\">Sabitha Frey</a> seized the undefended Harrenhal, she found only Alys within, with the wet nurse claiming to be pregnant with Aemond's child. Alys eventually escaped with Aemond when the prince returned to Harrenhal and chased away Sabitha.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Later in the civil war, the pregnant Alys watched the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_Above_the_Gods_Eye\" title=\"Battle Above the Gods Eye\">Battle Above the Gods Eye</a> atop <a href=\"/index.php/Kingspyre_Tower\" title=\"Kingspyre Tower\">Kingspyre Tower</a> in Harrenhal below. Aemond and Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a> were both slain in their duel in <a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/132_AC\" title=\"132 AC\">132&#160;AC</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">regency of Aegon III</a>, Alys gathered a number of <a href=\"/index.php/Broken_men\" title=\"Broken men\">broken men</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Outlaw\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Outlaw\">outlaws</a> to Harrenhal. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Tyland_Lannister\" title=\"Tyland Lannister\">Tyland Lannister</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, sent Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Regis_Groves\" title=\"Regis Groves\">Regis Groves</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Darry\" title=\"Damon Darry\">Damon Darry</a> with a hundred men to deal with the so-called \"<a href=\"/index.php/Witch\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Witch\">witch</a> queen\". Alys presented a boy to the knights, claiming that she was Aemond's widow and that the child was his trueborn son. Alys declared the boy was the rightful king and ordered Regis to submit to him. Refusing to kneel, Regis instead insulted Alys and her son. Regis abruptly died then under questionable circumstances, and Alys's followers forced Damon's host to retreat to <a href=\"/index.php/Darry\" title=\"Darry\">Darry</a>. When informed of Regis's death, the regents of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a> decided that a stronger force would be needed to deal with Alys's outlaws at Harrenhal. Their plans were interrupted by the outbreak of <a href=\"/index.php/Winter_Fever\" title=\"Winter Fever\">Winter Fever</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, however.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alys_Rivers%27s_son&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I have <a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">the dragon's</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> in me. I can feel his fires licking at my womb.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers\" title=\"Alys Rivers\">Alys Rivers</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Sabitha_Frey\" title=\"Sabitha Frey\">Sabitha Frey</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Regis</b>: A <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a>?<br />\n<b>Alys</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">His</a> trueborn son and heir, and the rightful king of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Regis_Groves\" title=\"Regis Groves\">Regis Groves</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers\" title=\"Alys Rivers\">Alys Rivers</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I do not kneel to <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastards</a>, much less the baseborn whelp of a <a href=\"/index.php/Kinslayer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kinslayer\">kinslayer</a> and a <a href=\"/index.php/Wet_nurse\" title=\"Wet nurse\">milk cow</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Regis_Groves\" title=\"Regis Groves\">Regis Groves</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers\" title=\"Alys Rivers\">Alys Rivers</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alys_Rivers%27s_son&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; h